ICFP'26: Call for Participation and Early Registration Reminder

The 31st ACM SIGPLAN International Conference on Functional Programming
(ICFP 2026) and affiliated events invite you to participate in a full week
dedicated to functional programming!

https://icfp26.sigplan.org

Indianapolis, Indiana, USA; Aug 24-29, 2026
Early Registration Open Until July 25

*Register here*: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/attending/registration

*Early registration discount* is available until *July 25*!
ICFP Overview

ICFP is a celebration of the art and science of functional programming,
providing a forum for researchers and developers to engage on a variety of
topics, from foundations to features, and from abstraction to application.

   -

   Accepted Papers: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/track/icfp-2026-icfp-papers
   -

   Registration: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/attending/registration (Early
   registration discount available until *July 25*!)
   -

   Venue: Indiana University Indianapolis
   https://icfp26.sigplan.org/venue/icfp-2026-venue1
   -

   Hotel Blocks: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/attending/hotel-blocks
   -

   Tutorials: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/track/icfp-2026-icfp-tutorials

Keynotes

Keynote speakers this year:

   -

   Edward Lee (UC Berkeley): "Deterministic Concurrency"
   -

   Lindsey Kuper (UC Santa Cruz): "Interpreters everywhere!"
   -

   Daan Leijen (Microsoft Research): "Efficient strong functional
   programming with effects and compiler guided reference counting"

More info: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/track/icfp-2026-icfp-keynotes
Co-Located Events

There are several events co-located with ICFP:

*Monday, August 24*

   - PLMW: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/PLMW-ICFP-2026
   - HOPE: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/hope-2026
   - miniKanren: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/minikanren-2026
   - FARM: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/farm-2026

*Tuesday-Thursday, August 25-27*

   - ICFP - Main conference

*Friday, August 28*

   - Haskell (Aug 28-29): https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/haskellsymp-2026
   - Erlang: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/erlang-2026
   - ML Family: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/mlfamilyworkshop-2026
   - LOPSTR+PPDP (Aug 27-29):
   https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/lopstr-ppdp-2026

*Saturday, August 29*

   - Haskell (Aug 28-29): https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/haskellsymp-2026
   - Scheme: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/scheme-2026
   - FUNARCH: https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/funarch-2026
   - LOPSTR+PPDP (Aug 27-29):
   https://icfp26.sigplan.org/home/lopstr-ppdp-2026

